      "source_repo": "ashvardanian/less_slow.cpp",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Playing around \"Less Slow\" coding practices in C++ 20, C, CUDA, PTX, & Assembly, from numerics & SIMD to coroutines, ranges, exception handling, networking and user-space IO"
